# Netlify redirects and rewrites

# SPA fallback - serve index.html for all routes
/*    /index.html   200

# Security redirects
/admin/*  https://timelyr.com/  301
/.env     https://timelyr.com/  301
/.git/*   https://timelyr.com/  301

# Legacy redirects (if migrating from another domain)
# https://old-domain.com/*  https://timelyr.com/:splat  301!

# Force HTTPS
http://timelyr.com/*  https://timelyr.com/:splat  301!
http://www.timelyr.com/*  https://timelyr.com/:splat  301!

# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.timelyr.com/*  https://timelyr.com/:splat  301!